Specimens studied: 
AMNH 5027: American Museum of Natural History, New York
; 
BHM 3033: Black Hills Museum, Hill City, South Dakota
; 
MOR 555: Museum of the Rockies, Bozeman, Montana
; 
SDSM 12047: South Dakota School of Mines, Rapid City, South Dakota
